      <title>三菱日联金融集团称将讨论购买 HDFC 部门 17 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/mufg-said-to-discuss-buying-1-7-billion-stake-in-hdfc-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，三菱日联金融集团 (Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group Inc.) 正在洽谈收购 HDFC Bank Ltd. 消费贷款部门约 17 亿美元的股份，以满足印度不断增长的个人融资贷款需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/mufg-said-to-discuss-buying-1-7-billion-stake-in-hdfc-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
