      <title>中广核新能源母公司称将重启私有化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-s-cgn-new-energy-s-parent-said-to-revive-take-private-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中广核新能源控股有限公司的母公司在三年多前放弃了之前的计划后，正在考虑将这家在香港上市的电力生产商私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-s-cgn-new-energy-s-parent-said-to-revive-take-private-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
